'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 66''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 66''',  was the sixty-sixth issue of ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', released on [[October 19]], [[2006]] and covering [[November]] and [[December]] 2006. It contained 100 pages.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Com-Scan]]"
*[[Best of Hyperspace|Jump to Hyperspace]]
*[[Jawa's Corner]]
*[[Scouting the Galaxy]] &mdash; The One That Almost Got Away {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 89}}
*[[Star Wars Q&A|Q&A]]
*[[Set Piece]] &mdash; Escape From Cloud City {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 89}}
*[[Comlink (department)|Com-Link]]

===Features===
*"[[Inspired by Empire]]" by [[Pete Vilmur]]
*"[[Where Did You Dig Up That Old Fossil?]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 89|''Star Wars Insider'' 89]]}}
*"[[ILM's Sizzling Mustafarian Summer]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 89}}
*"[[The Art of War (Star Wars Insider 89)|The Art of War]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 89}}
*"[[Underworld: A Galaxy of Scum and Villainy]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 89}}
*"[[Bricks, Whips, and Spaceships]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 89}}
*"[[The League of Spies]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 73|''Star Wars Insider'' 73]]}}
*"Inside the DVD Menus" by [[Pete Vilmur]]

